  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Goemon: Shin Sedai Shūmei! is a game in the Ganbare Goemon series released for the PlayStation on December 20, 2001 in Japan. It is a spin-off of the original Ganbare Goemon series.\nIn February 2002, a conversion of this game was released for the Game Boy Advance titled Goemon: New Age Shutsudō!, with various modifications and cuts made from the original PlayStation version.\n\nNeither version was released outside of Japan.",
